46:40.332 --> 46:41.959
[sighs]

47:11.321 --> 47:13.866
[flipping pages]

47:13.950 --> 47:15.826
[door bell dings]

47:31.008 --> 47:32.009
Hello.

47:33.970 --> 47:35.805
My name is Jonas.

47:35.888 --> 47:37.514
I know who you are.

47:37.598 --> 47:41.477
You know what they told you, and you
know what your senses are telling you.

47:41.560 --> 47:44.605
The question is, Will,
which of the two are you going to trust?

47:44.688 --> 47:46.148
How do you know my name?

47:46.231 --> 47:48.484
- She told me.
- Who?

47:48.567 --> 47:51.570
Angelica, the woman
that gave birth to you,

47:51.654 --> 47:53.489
just before she took her life.

47:53.572 --> 47:55.574
She shot herself.

47:55.658 --> 47:59.578
We all experience many births
and deaths during a life...

48:00.537 --> 48:04.792
but few know what it means
to be reborn a sensate.

48:04.875 --> 48:07.920
- A what?
- You have a migraine.

48:08.004 --> 48:09.922
You've had it since you saw her.

48:10.006 --> 48:11.799
It will last for several more days.

48:11.882 --> 48:15.011
When mine finally ended,
I cried like a baby,

48:15.093 --> 48:16.595
but that's just the beginning.

48:16.679 --> 48:18.555
You will start to feel strange things.

48:18.639 --> 48:21.017
You will feel snow
in the middle of the summer,

48:21.058 --> 48:24.061
rain when there isn't
a cloud in the sky.

48:24.144 --> 48:28.315
You'll feel anger and joy and pain.

48:29.149 --> 48:32.069
Pleasure without any reason.

48:33.737 --> 48:37.324
Excuse me. Excuse me.
Do you see this guy?

48:37.407 --> 48:39.493
I don't have much time, Will.

48:39.576 --> 48:42.038
There's a plane leaving in an hour
and I have to be on it.

48:42.120 --> 48:43.413
No, you're not going anywhere.

48:43.497 --> 48:45.958
There is a girl in San Francisco,
Nomi Marks.

48:46.042 --> 48:50.754
She needs your help,
just like Sara Patrell needed your help.

48:54.800 --> 48:57.094
I'm still a cop. I can't let you go.

48:57.177 --> 48:58.679
I'm not the enemy, Will.

48:58.762 --> 49:01.515
Quite a few governments
including this one says you are.

49:01.598 --> 49:04.935
You're about to go for the gun strapped
to your ankle, but by the time you do,

49:05.019 --> 49:07.437
the fight will be over.

49:10.148 --> 49:11.942
[Will grunts]

49:18.615 --> 49:20.367
[door bell dings]

49:21.326 --> 49:23.120
Not cool, man.
Should I call the cops?

49:23.203 --> 49:24.955
[Will] I am a cop.

49:25.039 --> 49:27.041
[tires screeching]

49:42.723 --> 49:45.059
[tires screech]

50:09.291 --> 50:11.877
- Don't do this, Will.
- What the fuck?!

50:11.961 --> 50:14.379
You've spent your life trying
to understand what happened to you.

50:14.463 --> 50:16.882
If you don't let me go,
you might never find out.

50:16.966 --> 50:20.594
- Oh, my God, I'm losing my mind.
- No, it's just expanding.

50:21.011 --> 50:22.846
[crashing]

50:34.108 --> 50:36.110
[Jonas laughs]

50:37.903 --> 50:39.780
Well done.

50:39.863 --> 50:44.118
Yes, the connection flows both ways,
which raises the question:

50:44.201 --> 50:46.703
If you're here,
who's driving back there?

50:57.214 --> 50:59.967
- [tires screeching]
- [crashing]

51:03.679 --> 51:06.849
[dance song playing]
